snippet.title: Pokémon Blue (GB) - Longplay
snippet.description:
Originally recorded for https://www.longplays.org

Played by: Mariofan98

To mark the 20th anniversary of Pokemon is here the Longplay of Pokemon Blue played on BizHawk in perfect quality.
Glitchless almost MissingNo. Spazbo has beaten Red 2010 so i have to defeat now the new champ Spazbo. #Pokemon20
And for Spazbo: Sorry that your name is the name of the rival.
